May means warmer days, colorful blooms and Mother’s Day celebrations all month long!! 🌸

If cooking up goodness is your love language, these peach yogurt crepes say it best! 💕

These homemade crepes are light, luscious, and filled with a dreamy whipped Savannah’s Peach yogurt cream (made with our farm-fresh skyr, of course 😉).

Comment ‘Crepe’ & we’ll send you the full recipe so you whip up some deliciousness this Mother’s Day! 🧑‍🍳
